    <h1>
      Backstop Mobile
    </h1>

    <p>
      Backstop Mobile is an extension of the Backstop CRM product. It provides on the go access to the core functionality of the platform. The project started as a dream between my CTO, an engineer and myself to revamp our tired Blackberry optimized mobile web service. I created the intial pitch deck that was passed around and garnered attention for the project.
    </p>
