    <p>
      Fast forward a few months, and Backstop began consulting with <a href="http://www.solstice-mobile.com/" >Solstice Mobile</a> in a joint effort to release a hybrid app on both the iOS and Android platforms. We brought in the external team to shorten our product to market time and have access to their mobile expertise. This was a very fast and agile product delivery and a wonderful experience working with team members from both companies sharing process, offices, and best practices. We worked with an interdisciplinary team to develop sophisticated yet intuitive interactions and design patterns, continually user experience testing out our iterations using interactive Balsamiq wireframes, user testing, and feedback forums.
    </p>
    <div class="call-out bm-comps">
    </div>
    <ul class="bxslider2">
