    <p>
      A big piece of the application was not only allowing our users to retrieve information on the go, but giving them the ability to add new entities and data into the system. The team heavily iterated over the form fields and creation aspect of the application.  We worked through a range of designs and formats and delivered clean reusable patterns for each type of data.  Single line inputs, multi selectors, phone inputs and text blocks were all treated as unique experiences and optimized for the most efficient workflow.
    </p>
