      As Lead Product Designer I worked on wire-frames, interaction design, user experience, and a design compositions for the application. I interfaced between internal stakeholders, product management, the scrum master, and the engineers to bring out the final design and interactions for the application.  My final deliverables were redlined designs, native assets, and a new SVG icon library for the hybrid portion of the application.
    </p>
